snippet.title: Arcade Game: Pin Pong (1974 Atari) no sound
snippet.description:
The first ever video game based pinball game ever created.

Any interested in trying out this game, here it is:
http://adamulation.blogspot.com/

Note: Comments for gameplay videos with no sound are now disable because they video is subject to be reuploaded when ever sound is addedto the game. Once the sound has been added, it will be reuploaded and comments will be enabled.
